OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FWatch Kris Jepson's report on the
OL,7,FKane's World Foundation workshops in
OL,8,FDarlington's Cornmill Shopping Centre.
OL,10,FThe mother of a boy with autism has
OL,11,Fdelivered training workshops to staff
OL,12,Fat 25 businesses and organisations in
OL,13,FDarlington to ensure they are more
OL,14,F"kind" and "understanding" to families
OL,15,Fwith children who have special
OL,16,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,17,F(SEND).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
