FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FKelly Knight set up Kane's World
OL,7,FFoundation in 2025, after years of
OL,8,Fnegative experiences when taking her 7-
OL,9,Fyear old son, Kane, to public places.
OL,11,FKane has autism, is non-verbal and
OL,12,Fstruggles to regulate his emotions in
OL,13,Fcertain environments. Kelly explained:
OL,15,F"In an environment that was crowded he
OL,16,Fgets extremely overwhelmed and his
OL,17,Fresponse to that would be fight, where
OL,18,FI would get kicked, punched, hair
OL,19,Fpulled.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,F"It goes from nought to fifty really,
OL,7,Freally quickly, and that could be
OL,8,Fperceived by somebody who doesn't have
OL,9,Fthat understanding that he's just a
OL,10,Fnaughty child."
OL,12,FKelly set up Kane's World Foundation
OL,13,Fto deliver the training workshops to
OL,14,Ftackle the negative reactions her
OL,15,Ffamily have experienced.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FShe added: "You get the tuts, you get
OL,7,Fthe stares, you can hear the whispers,
OL,8,Fand we're not in a position to respond
OL,9,Fto everything, because we're trying to
OL,10,Fmanage and keep our children safe in
OL,11,Fthat moment."
OL,13,FThe workshop advocates for quiet
OL,14,Fspaces, planned quiet times, and
OL,15,Ffidget toy bags to stimulate the
OL,16,Fchildren with an activity.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
