OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FAttending one workshop at the Cornmill
OL,7,FShopping Centre in Darlington,
OL,8,FSeineade Stainsby, who runs a health
OL,9,Fand beauty shop, said: "It was really
OL,10,Finformative. Kelly's really given me a
OL,11,Flot of knowledge on what I can do in
OL,12,Fmy shop to help just alleviate any
OL,13,Fproblems that they have with the
OL,14,Fchildren."
OL,16,FThe chairman of Darling RFC, Andrew
OL,17,FGunnell, also attended and although
OL,18,Fhis sports club throws out different
OL,19,Fchallenges, he did see some beneficial
OL,20,Fchanges that could be made to welcome
OL,21,FSEND families more.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FHe added: "It's a completely different
OL,7,Fconcept to do it on a grass pitch,
OL,8,Fwith a team, than it is one family,
OL,9,Fshopping in a store, but there's
OL,10,Fthings that we've already spoken to
OL,11,FKelly about how we can take her ideas,
OL,12,Ftwist them, adapt them, develop them,
OL,13,Fand make them work for us in that
OL,14,Fsports environment."
OL,16,FAlex Blackham has already incorporated
OL,17,Fthe skills in his cafe and said the
OL,18,Ffidget toy bags Kelly gave him have
OL,19,Fhad a real positive impact on SEND
OL,20,Fchildren who have visited his business.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1784557137
OL,3,CWorkshops for businesses encouraging
OL,4,C'kindness' for SEND families
OL,6,FHe said: "(in the past we may have
OL,7,Fbeen) thinking it's a naughty child or
OL,8,Fthinking it's a very bad parent, (but)
OL,9,Fnow we can learn to recognise that we
OL,10,Fmaybe shouldn't be making those
OL,11,Fdecisions. "
OL,13,FKane's World Foundation has so far
OL,14,Ftrained 25 organisations in the area
OL,15,Fand with lottery funding hopes to
OL,16,Fextend the offer even further afield.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
